OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe report, produced with the help of
OL,8,FThe University of Bristol and Cardiff
OL,9,FUniversity, found weather-related
OL,10,Fdisasters have increased 400% in the
OL,11,Flast 50 years. The increase has been
OL,12,Flinked to man-made climate change.
OL,14,FHere are 112 of the world's biggest
OL,15,Fcities. The darker the red, the faster
OL,16,Fthey're drying. The darker the blue,
OL,17,Fthe wetter they're getting.
OL,19,FAll of Europe's biggest cities are
OL,20,Fbecoming more prone to drought.
