OL,7,FSouthern Asian cities are at an
OL,8,Fincreasing risk of floods.
OL,10,F"This research comes at a pivotal
OL,11,Ftime, as we're seeing a sweep of
OL,12,Fglobal aid cuts, which could leave
OL,13,Fbasic human rights hanging in the
OL,14,Fbalance," said Tim Wainwright,
OL,15,FWaterAid UK's Chief Executive.
