OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FAnd it's a similar story in London -
OL,8,Fthe only UK city analysed. Whilst the
OL,9,Flevel of drying is quite mild, our
OL,10,Fwater defences and storage aren't
OL,11,Fgreat. A small example, but we haven't
OL,12,Fopened a single new reservoir in the
OL,13,Fpast 30 years.
